Phrase.create!(english: 'Are you taking any medication? (drops, ointments, capsules, pills)', traditional: '你現在有沒有固定用藥？（眼藥水，藥膏，膠囊，藥丸）', pinyin: 'nǐ xiàn zài yǒu méi yǒu gù dìng yòng yào     yǎn yào shuǐ   yào gāo   jiāo náng   yào wán', list: history)
Phrase.create!(english: 'Do you feel something in your eye?', traditional: '你覺得有沒有東西在眼睛𥚃面?', pinyin: 'nǐ jué dé yǒu méi yǒu dōng xī zài yǎn jīng  li  miàn', list: history)
Phrase.create!(english: 'Do you have any allergies?', traditional: '你有沒有過敏症狀？', pinyin: 'nǐ yǒu méi yǒu guò mǐn zhèng zhuàng', list: history)
Phrase.create!(english: 'Are you allergic to certain medicines?', traditional: '你有沒有對哪些藥物過敏？', pinyin: 'nǐ yǒu méi yǒu duì nǎ xiē yào wù guò mǐn', list: history)
Phrase.create!(english: 'For what reason do you take the medicines?', traditional: '你為什麼要吃這些藥？', pinyin: 'nǐ wèi shén me yào chī zhè xiē yào', list: history)
Phrase.create!(english: 'Do you drink a lot of alcohol?', traditional: '你平常有沒有喝很多酒？', pinyin: 'nǐ píng cháng yǒu méi yǒu hē hěn duō jiǔ', list: history)
Phrase.create!(english: 'Do you smoke? How much?', traditional: '你有沒有抽煙？多少量？', pinyin: 'nǐ yǒu méi yǒu chōu yān   duō shǎo liàng', list: history)
Phrase.create!(english: 'Do you take narcotics or sedatives or both?', traditional: '你有沒有習慣用麻醉藥、鎮定劑，還是兩種都用？', pinyin: 'nǐ yǒu méi yǒu xí guàn yòng má zuì yào   zhèn dìng jì   hái shì liǎng zhǒng dōu yòng', list: history)
Phrase.create!(english: 'Are you nervous?', traditional: '你會緊張嗎？', pinyin: 'nǐ huì jǐn zhāng ma', list: history)
Phrase.create!(english: 'Have you been under a doctor\'s care before?', traditional: '你以前有看過眼科醫生嗎？', pinyin: 'nǐ yǐ qián yǒu kàn guò yǎn kē yī shēng ma', list: history)
Phrase.create!(english: 'What is his name, address, and telephone number?', traditional: '他的名字，地址，和電話號碼是甚麼？', pinyin: 'tā de míng zì   dì zhǐ   hé diàn huà hào mǎ shì shén me', list: history)
Phrase.create!(english: 'How old are you?', traditional: '你現在幾歲？', pinyin: 'nǐ xiàn zài jǐ suì', list: history)
Phrase.create!(english: 'Please take off your glasses.', traditional: '請你把眼鏡拿掉。', pinyin: 'qǐng nǐ bǎ yǎn jìng ná diào', list: history)
Phrase.create!(english: 'Please put them on.', traditional: '請戴起來。', pinyin: 'qǐng dài qǐ lái', list: history)
Phrase.create!(english: 'Describe (show me) what you see.', traditional: '請描述（告訴我）你看到的東西。', pinyin: 'qǐng miáo shù   gào sù wǒ   nǐ kàn dào de dōng xī', list: history)
Phrase.create!(english: 'Do you see lightning flashes or lights and stars above the objects?', traditional: '你有沒有看到閃光還是亮點在物體上面？', pinyin: 'nǐ yǒu méi yǒu kàn dào shǎn guāng hái shì liàng diǎn zài wù tǐ shàng miàn', list: history)
Phrase.create!(english: 'Is it fleeting or is it constant?', traditional: '是暫時的還是持久的？', pinyin: 'shì zàn shí de hái shì chí jiǔ de', list: history)
Phrase.create!(english: 'Do you see it constantly or sometimes not at all?', traditional: '你能一直看的到它或者是有時一點都看不到？', pinyin: 'nǐ néng yī zhí kàn de dào tā huò zhě shì yǒu shí yī diǎn dōu kàn bù dào', list: history)
Phrase.create!(english: 'Do you see anything appearing like a snowfall?', traditional: '你有沒有看東西看起來像下雪一樣？', pinyin: 'nǐ yǒu méi yǒu kàn dōng xī kàn qǐ lái xiàng xià xuě yī yàng', list: history)
Phrase.create!(english: 'Do you see a dark cloud or have you seen one?', traditional: '你有沒有看過黑色隂影？', pinyin: 'nǐ yǒu méi yǒu kàn guò hēi sè yīn yǐng', list: history)
Phrase.create!(english: 'At times, do the objects appear distorted?', traditional: '有時候東西會不會看起來很扭曲？', pinyin: 'yǒu shí hòu dōng xī huì bù huì kàn qǐ lái hěn niǔ qū', list: history)
