Phrase.create!(english: 'Does it seem like a shade is being held over your eyes?', traditional: '在看東西時會不會像戴帽子一樣有帽沿遮擋你的視線？', pinyin: 'zài kàn dōng xī shí huì bù huì xiàng dài mào zi yī yàng yǒu mào yán zhē dǎng nǐ de shì xiàn', list: history)
