Phrase.create!(english: 'You will not be able to see up close for a couple of hours, is that a problem?', traditional: '你幾個小時都不能看近的東西很清楚，這樣有沒有問題？', pinyin: 'nǐ jǐ gè xiǎo shí dōu bù néng kàn jìn de dōng xī hěn qīng chǔ zhè yàng yǒu méi yǒu wèn tí', list: internals)
Phrase.create!(english: 'I am going to put drops in your eyes.', traditional: '我現在就放眼藥了。', pinyin: 'wǒ xiàn zài jiù fàng yǎn yào le', list: internals)
